{"tid":441894,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[勸世post]切勿進入此店飲周打湯","createTime":"2017-10-20T05:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T15:40:17.000Z","uid":147430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c092b6bca95aa0181972c1fb4e28f5c081dd5357","tid":441894,"uid":147430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:57:09.000Z","msg":"古語有云，要分一間餐廳好壞，飲佢既湯就可分端倪。<br />\n呢間咁嘅店周打湯仲要白到同隻碟一樣色，稀到同杯茶一樣稀。Lunch時間去食仲要檸茶檸水都冇，仲要話廚房做唔切，淨係可以叫果汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢兜咁既湯仲好意思收人8蚊，我去百佳買罐溝都好過佢。價錢不是重點，重點係食完之後好似有種引人中伏既感覺。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/20/135532_bfcd8431c24e1f068d274d23580e4d43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2F135532_bfcd8431c24e1f068d274d23580e4d43.jpg&h=28125949&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/20/135534_7e8a5dacbef67f9b12ef09e106c362b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2F135534_7e8a5dacbef67f9b12ef09e106c362b9.jpg&h=c3c816ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"671e4eef0c4df883cf608ad987086a3b469688b7","tid":441894,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf2cf6e8a153c306e04c34c2ffe7e6726e5a0a7","tid":441894,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:11:08.000Z","msg":"好多香港飲食業商家都畀緊屎我地食"},{"pid":"859456057b9aaeb76bcfc350e8a109a6aa071058","tid":441894,"uid":147430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:12:19.000Z","msg":"大家小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84a5ab56cfba687987debb57c0719d9bd8806f2","tid":441894,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"雞翼唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca9e92c242ebd6f37130deadd035ca26104e833","tid":441894,"uid":16623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:51:51.000Z","msg":"碗湯成碗椰汁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbf4e1b04d9ee72d0470583ade4ce65c7bec8cc","tid":441894,"uid":147430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726e7ec4b018e4bc3543d9bde15c0f4f869e1df5","tid":441894,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"呢間餐廳之前係天水圍開過<br />\n唔夠半年就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家個位變咗雲貴軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}